":[\"tebigatzaly1_1717651789.jpg\",\"diorama2skabanom_1718172238.jpg\",\"griby_1718172483.jpg\",\"\"],\"title\":[\"\",\"\",\"\",\"\"]}','<p><img src=\"images/advportfoliopro/images/tebigatzaly.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"410\" height=\"342\" /></p>','','',0,'',0),(5,9,'Sungat bölümi','sekilendiris','<hr />\r\n<p>Häzirki döwürde türkmen sungaty halkyň çeperçilik medeniýeti pajarlap ösýär we türkmen halkynyň ruhy dünýägaraýşynyň esasy çeşmeleriniň biri bolup durýar. Muzeýiň sungat ekspozisiýasynda dürli görnüşli nakgaş, grafika eserleri, keramika, heýkeltaraşlyk işleri ýerleşdirilen. Bu sungat eserlerinde türkmen halkynyň milli aýratynlyklary, gadymy we häzirki zaman däp-dessurlary we halkyň şöhratly taryhy beýan edilýär. Dürli reňkleriň öwüşgünlerinde döredilen bu ajaýyp eserler türkmen tebigatynyň gözelliklerini açyp görkezýär. Olarda oba zähmetkeşleriniň durmuşy, zenanlaryň keşbi hem öz beýanyny tapýar. Bu sungat eserleri ösüp gelýän ýaş nesilleri watansöýüjilik ruhunda terbiýelemekde we şöhratly geçmişi öwrenmekde çeşme bolup durýar. Taryhy döwürleri, halkyň gahrymançylykly geçmişini şeýle-de taryhy şahsyýetleri görkezýän suratlar tomaşaçylarda aýratyn gyzyklanma döredýär. Ekspozisiýanyň dowamynda keramika sungatyna hem aýratyn orun berilýär.</p>\r\n<p>«Sungat»  älemi  adamzadyň  kalbyna şatlyk çaýýan, ynsan ruhuna  ruh goşup, adamzadyň aň-düşünjesini, arzuwlaryny jadylaýjy ajaýyp dünýäsine gaplap alýan,  ýagşy  niýetlere  atarýan äpet  täsirli güýiçdir. Garaşsyzlyk döwrüniň sungatynda öňde goýulýan wezipeleriň gerimi giňeýär.    Halkyň  «ruhy  galkynyşy»  sungatda şöhlelenýär.</p>\r\n<p>Eserlerde millilik, arassa ahlakçylyk, parasatlyk, gaýduwsyzlyk ýaly häsiýetler şöhlelendirilýär. M.Gubyýewiň <em> </em>«Gökdepe», Ý.Kuliýewiň <em> </em>«Kerwen», K.Begenjowyň «Umyt» atly nakgaş eserleri, M.Işangulyýewanyň «Geçmişe uzaýan ýol», N.Seýtiýewiň «Kerwen» atly heýkel eserlerinde türkmen halkynyň taryhyny we medeniýetini beýan edýär. Ekzpozisiýanyň dowamynda O.Gulhanowanyň, G.Baýryýewanyň, J.Bazarowanyň keramika eserleri özüniň nepisligi bilen tapawutlanýar.</p>\r\n<p>Dünýäniň çar ýanyna ýaýran türkmenleriň aýdym-saz sungaty umumytürki halklarynyň aýdym-saz sungatynyň aýrylmaz bir şahasy bolup durýar. Halkymyzyň uzak taryhynyň akymyndan  gözbaş alan ruhy medeniýetimizde aýdymdyr-sazlaryň uly hormata mynasypdygy ýokary derejede döredilen mukamlar muňa şaýatlyk edýär. Türkmen halkynyň häzirki döwre çenli gadymdan gelýän dutar (tamdyra), gyjak, tüýdük (ýedi bogun, dilli tüýdük, şadyýan tüýdük), gopuz ýaly saz gurallary bolupdyr.</p>\r\n<p>Muzeýi görmäge gelen tomaşaçylar üçin täze tehnologiýalaryň kömegi bilen bu ýerde türkmen sungatyna degişli bolan gymmatlyklar bilen bilelikde şol sungatda ýerine ýetirilýän aýdym-sazyň owazyny diňlemek mümkinçiliginden peýdalanyp bilýärler. Ýagny tomaşaçy dutar, gyjak, gargy tüýdük saz gurallarynyň ýanyna baranlarynda şol sungaty owazy bolup ýaňlanýan mukamy diňläp bilýärler.</p>',1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',3,1,'tk-TM','2023-04-18 09:36:45',704,'','2024-06-12 06:30:06',731,'{\"show_title\":\"\",\"show_description\":\"\",\"description_position\":\"bottom\",\"description_width\":\"11\",\"image_width\":\"\",\"image_height\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\"}','','','{\"robots\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\"}','{\"image\":[\"sungat1_1717738386.jpg\",\"sungat2_1717738478.jpg\",\"sungatzaly.jpg\",\"\"],\"title\":[\"\",\"\",\"\",\"\"]}','<p><img src=\"images/advportfoliopro/images/sungatzaly.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"410\" height=\"342\" /></p>','','',0,'',0),(7,9,'Hall of Fine Arts','hall-of-fine-arts','<hr />\r\n<p>The Hall of Fine Arts is a place where you can enjoy unique works of art created by masters of different eras and styles. Paintings, graphics, sculptures and other works that reflect the culture and traditions of peoples living in Turkmenistan are displayed here.</p>\r\n<p>You can find works of art created by national artists, enjoy the beauty of national costumes presented in paintings and learn unique motifs and symbols used by artists in their works.</p>\r\n<p>The Hall of Fine Arts exhibit includes not only beautiful paintings and sculptures, but also the unique stories behind the creation of each piece. You can learn about the creative methods and techniques that the artists used to create their works, and how their ideas reflect the culture and traditions of the Turkmen people.</p>\r\n<p>The Hall of Fine Arts is a place where you can spend quality time and have an unforgettable experience. It is a must-see for tourists, as well as for anyone interested in the art and culture of the Turkmen people.</p>',1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',2,1,'en-GB','2023-04-18 09:36:45',704,'','2024-06-12 06:30:36',731,'{\"show_title\":\"\",\"show_description\":\"\",\"description_position\":\"bottom\",\"description_width\":\"11\",\"image_width\":\"\",\"image_height\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\"}','','','{\"robots\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\"}','{\"image\":[\"port4.jpg\",\"port4.jpg\",\"port4.jpg\",\"\"],\"title\":[\"\",\"\",\"\",\"\"]}','<p><img src=\"images/advportfoliopro/images/sungatzaly.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"410\" height=\"342\" /></p>','','',0,'',0),(8,9,'Зал природы края','2023-05-06-06-26-07','				<hr />\r\n<p>Зал природы края - это уникальное место, где посетители могут познакомиться с разнообразием флоры и фауны, произрастающих и обитающих на территории Туркменистана. Экспозиция зала охватывает множество видов животных и растений, которые характерны для природных условий Туркменистана.</p>\r\n<p>Экспозиция зала природы края в музее Туркменистана включает в себя множество интерактивных элементов, которые позволяют посетителям более глубоко понять природу и ее взаимосвязь с окружающей средой. Вы сможете пройти по модели ландшафта и узнать о том, какие растения и животные обитают в разных климатических зонах Туркменистана.</p>\r\n<p>Зал природы края в музее Туркменистана - это обязательное место для посещения для всех, кто интересуется экологией и природой. Это место, где вы сможете насладиться красотой и разнообразием местной природы, а также узнать о том, как сохранить и защитить ее для будущих поколений.</p>',1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',5,1,'ru-RU','2023-04-18 09:35:31',704,'','2024-08-15 11:40:45',704,'{\"show_title\":\"\",\"show_description\":\"\",\"description_position\":\"bottom\",\"description_width\":\"11\",\"image_width\":\"\",\"image_height\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\"}','','','{\"robots\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\"}','{\"image\":[\"diorama2skabanom_1718172238.jpg\",\"etno2_1717738938.jpg\",\"\"],\"title\":[\"\",\"\",\"\"]}','<p><img src=\"images/advportfoliopro/images/tebigatzaly.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"410\" height=\"342\" /></p>','','',0,'',0),(9,9,'Hall of Nature of the Region','hall-of-nature-of-the-region','<hr />\r\n<p>The Nature Hall is a unique place where visitors can get acquainted with the diversity of flora and fauna growing and inhabiting the territory of Turkmenistan. The exposition of the Hall covers many species of animals and plants which are characteristic of the natural conditions of Turkmenistan.</p>\r\n<p>The exposition of the nature hall in the Museum of Turkmenistan includes many interactive elements that enable visitors to gain a deeper understanding of nature and its interrelationship with the environment. You will be able to walk through a landscape model and learn about what plants and animals inhabit different climatic zones of Turkmenistan.</p>\r\n<p>The Nature Hall at Turkmenistan Museum is a must-see for anyone interested in ecology and nature. This is a place where you can enjoy the beauty and diversity of local nature, and learn how to preserve and protect it for future generations.</p>',1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',4,1,'en-GB','2023-04-18 09:35:31',704,'','2024-06-12 06:34:05',731,'{\"show_title\":\"\",\"show_description\":\"\",\"description_position\":\"bottom\",\"description_width\":\"11\",\"image_width\":\"\",\"image_height\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\"}','','','{\"robots\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\"}','{\"image\":[\"port5.jpg\",\"po