larymyzyň we urp-adatlarynyň a&yacute;awly saklanylmagynda, milli &yacute;&ouml;relgelerimiziň dowam etmeginde, edepli-ekramly nesilleriň kemala gelmeginde zenanlarymyzyň hyzmaty uludyr. T&uuml;rkmen zenanlarynyň başarjaň elleriniň aja&yacute;yp sungaty bolan ke&ccedil;eler biziň &yacute;urdumyzyň taryhynda &ouml;&ccedil;mejek yz galdyrypdyr. Arkadag ş&auml;heriniň Taryhy we &uuml;lk&auml;ni &ouml;wreniş muze&yacute;inde hem &ldquo;Zenanlar &yacute;aşa&yacute;şyň g&ouml;zelligi&rdquo; atly gepleşik ge&ccedil;irildi.T&uuml;rkmen zenanlarynyň zehin-başarnygynyň, irginsiz z&auml;hmetiniň miwesi bolan bu senetleri synlanyňda, aja&yacute;yp bir du&yacute;gyny başdan ge&ccedil;ir&yacute;&auml;rsiň. &Ccedil;&uuml;nki g&ouml;zelliklerden zynatly, &ouml;z&uuml;ne &ccedil;ekiji, m&auml;hir-yhlasdan doly bolan bu senet durşuna ykbal hem sungatdyr. T&uuml;rkmen zenanlary &auml;hli d&ouml;w&uuml;rde-de el işlerini nusgalyk derejede s&uuml;nn&auml;l&auml;pdirler. El h&uuml;n&auml;rini eneden-gyza ge&ccedil;irip dowam etdiripdirler. &Yacute;yllar ge&ccedil;digi&ccedil;e, olara t&auml;ze-t&auml;ze &ouml;w&uuml;şginler &ccedil;a&yacute;ylypdyr. Gelin-gyzlar el işlerini her d&ouml;w&uuml;rde-de nusgalyk derejede s&uuml;nn&auml;l&auml;pdirler. El h&uuml;n&auml;rini nesilden-nesle ge&ccedil;irip, dowam etdiripdirler.Bu sungat asyrlar aşyp, &yacute;yllar ge&ccedil;digi&ccedil;e, t&auml;ze r&ouml;w&uuml;şlere beslenip, has-da k&auml;milleşdiril&yacute;&auml;r. Zenanlaryň el işlerinde olaryň &ccedil;&auml;ksiz ussatlygy, irginsiz z&auml;hmeti, yhlasy g&ouml;r&uuml;n&yacute;&auml;r. &Ccedil;eper elli zenanlar nagyşlara &ouml;z halkynyň taryhyny, g&ouml;w&uuml;n matlabyny, arzuw-hy&yacute;allaryny siňdirip bilipdirler. Halkyň g&uuml;ndelik durmuşynda giňden ulanylan we ruhy d&uuml;n&yacute;&auml;sine siňen ke&ccedil;elerimiz h&auml;zirki wagtda-da &yacute;urdumyzyň d&uuml;rli k&uuml;njeklerinde &yacute;aşamagyny dowam etdir&yacute;&auml;r. Biziň halkymyzyň arasynda oňa hi&ccedil; wagt &auml;hmi&yacute;etini &yacute;itirmejek milli sungat h&ouml;km&uuml;nde garal&yacute;ar. Milli sungatymyzy, taryhymyzy, medeni&yacute;etimizi &ouml;wrnmekde we olara &yacute;aş nesillere giňden wagyz etmekde uly tagallalar ed&yacute;&auml;n t&uuml;rkmen halkynyň milli lideri Gahryman Arkadagymyza we Arkadagly Gahryman Serdarymyzyň janlary sag, &ouml;m&uuml;rleri uzak bolsun! Il-&yacute;urt b&auml;hbitli, b&uuml;tind&uuml;n&yacute;&auml; adamzat &auml;hmi&yacute;etli be&yacute;ik işleri hemişe rowa&ccedil;lyklara beslensin!</p>',1,11,'2024-08-14 05:52:36',731,'','2024-08-14 10:19:49',731,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','2024-08-12 05:52:36','0000-00-00 00:00:00','{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}','{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}','{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_image\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_image_alt_txt\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_article_format\":\"gallery\",\"helix_ultimate_audio\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_gallery\":\"{\\\"helix_ulti