 guwandyryjy netijeleridir. Arkadag şäheriniň Taryhy we ülkäni öwreniş muzeýinde Saçly Dursunowa adyndaky Arkadag şäheriniň lukmançylyk orta hünär okuw mekdebiniň talyplarynyň hem-de Arkadag şäheriniň 3-nji orta mekdebiniň okuwçylarynyň gatnaşmagynda  muzeýe gezelenç gurnaldy. \r\n   Munuň üçin bagtyýar nesillerimiziň Gahryman Arkadagymyza, peder ýoluny mynasyp dowam etdirýän Arkadagly Serdarymyza hoşallygynyň çägi ýokdur. Ýaş nesillerimize döwrebap bilim bermek üçin ähli şertleri döredip berýän türkmen halkynyň milli lideri Gahryman Arkadagymyzyň, Hormatly Prezidentimiz Arkadagly Gahryman Serdarymyzyň janlary sag, ömürleri uzak, il-ýurt bähbitli  bütindünýä adamzat ähmiýetli beýik işleri hemişe rowana ýollarda rowaçlyklara beslensin!\r\n',1,11,'2024-09-01 09:30:29',731,'','2024-08-31 09:55:28',731,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','2024-09-01 09:30:29','0000-00-00 00:00:00','{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}','{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}','{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"s