":\"\",\"xs_col\":\"\",\"tablet_order\":\"\",\"mobile_order\":\"\",\"hidden_xs\":\"\",\"hidden_sm\":\"\",\"hidden_md\":\"\",\"animationduration\":\"300\",\"animationdelay\":\"0\"},\"addons\":[{\"id\":1681731819685,\"name\":\"text_block\",\"visibility\":true,\"settings\":{\"admin_label\":\"\",\"title\":\"About our museum\",\"heading_selector\":\"h3\",\"title_fontsize\":{\"md\":\"45\",\"sm\":\"\",\"xs\":\"\"},\"title_lineheight\":{\"md\":\"\",\"sm\":\"\",\"xs\":\"\"},\"title_letterspace\":\"0\",\"text\":\"<p>Local history museum of Arkadag city presents the rich history and culture of the Akhal velayat and is a precious treasury of the national heritage.</p>\\n<p>ЭThe museum\'s exhibitions include archaeological finds, works of art, national costumes, household items and other artefacts, which reflect various stages of the history and culture of the Akhal velayat. Special attention is paid to the exhibits related to the traditional culture and way of life of the Turkmen people such as carpets, fabrics, jewellery and other unique items which are the national pride of Turkmenistan.</p>\\n<p>There are also many exhibits associated with the history of Turkmenistan\'s development, its economic and social achievements, as well as modern trends in its development. Visitors can get acquainted with museum\'s collection by visiting numerous halls and exhibition areas where exhibits are arranged chronologically and according to thematic categories.</p>\\n<p>The museum is also of interest to nature and science lovers. There is a whole section devoted to the nature of Akhal velayat including whole collections of animals and plants inhabiting and growing on the territory of velayat.</p>\\n<p>Turkmenistan Museum is not only a collection of exhibits but also a centre of education and research. The museum hosts various events including lectures, seminars and exhibitions that attract researchers, scientists and students from all over the world. The Arkadagh Museum also hosts cultural and educational events such as conferences, seminars and exhibitions. With its rich history and culture, the museum plans to attract researchers, scholars, students and tourists from around the world to discover Turkmenistan\'s heritage and traditions.</p>\\n<p>Overall, the Arkadag City History and Local History Museum is an important site of national culture and history that embodies the richness and diversity of the Akhal velayat.</p>\",\"alignment\":\"\",\"text_fontsize\":{\"md\":\"16\",\"sm\":\"\",\"xs\":\"\"},\"text_lineheight\":\"\",\"text_fontweight\":\"\",\"dropcap\":0,\"class\":\"\",\"global_background_type\":\"none\",\"global_background_gradient\":{\"color\":\"#00c6fb\",\"color2\":\"#005bea\",\"deg\":\"45\",\"type\":\"linear\"},\"global_background_image\":{\"src\":\"\"},\"global_background_repeat\":\"no-repeat\",\"global_background_size\":\"cover\",\"global_background_attachment\":\"inherit\",\"global_background_position\":\"50% 50%\",\"global_use_overlay\":0,\"global_overlay_type\":\"overlay_none\",\"global_gradient_overlay\":{\"color\":\"rgba(127, 0, 255, 0.8)\",\"color2\":\"rgba(225, 0, 255, 0.7)\",\"deg\":\"45\",\"type\":\"linear\"},\"global_pattern_overlay\":{\"src\":\"\"},\"global_overlay_pattern_color\":\"\",\"blend_mode\":\"normal\",\"global_user_border\":0,\"global_border_width\":\"\",\"global_border_radius\":0,\"global_margin\":{\"md\":\"0px 0px 30px 0px\",\"sm\":\"   \",\"xs\":\"   \"},\"global_padding\":{\"md\":\"   \",\"sm\":\"   \",\"xs\":\"   \"},\"global_boxshadow\":\"0 0 0 0 #ffffff\",\"global_use_animation\":0,\"global_animationduration\":\"300\",\"global_animationdelay\":\"0\",\"global_custom_css\":\".sppb-addon-title{\\ntext-align: center;\\n}\\n.sppb-addon-content{\\ntext-indent: 40px;\\n}\",\"global_custom_position\":0,\"global_seclect_position\":\"relative\",\"global_addon_position_left\":{\"unit\":\"px\"},\"global_addon_position_top\":{\"unit\":\"px\"},\"use_global_width\":\"0\",\"hidden_md\":\"0\",\"hidden_sm\":\"0\",\"hidden_xs\":\