i\\u00a0 Arkadag \\u015f\\u00e4herini\\u0148 Taryhy we \\u00fclk\\u00e4ni \\u00f6wreni\\u015f muze\\u00fdinde \\u00abBagty\\u00fdar d\\u00f6wr\\u00fc\\u0148 bagtly \\u00e7agalary\\u00bb atly sergi gurnaldy. Bagty\\u00fdar durmu\\u015fy\\u0148 r\\u00f6w\\u015fen geljegi bolan g\\u00fclme\\u0148iz balajyklary\\u0148 sagdyn we ruhubelent \\u00f6smegi ugrunda ata Watanymyzda uly i\\u015fler alnyp baryl\\u00fdar.T\\u00fcrkmen halkymyz \\u015fan-\\u015f\\u00f6hratly taryhyny\\u0148 dowamynda \\u00f6z\\u00fcni\\u0148 milli gymmatlyklaryna,\\u00a0 ynsanperwer \\u00fdol-\\u00fd\\u00f6relgelerine e\\u00fdermek bilen, \\u00f6s\\u00fcp gel\\u00fd\\u00e4n \\u00fda\\u015f nesilleri\\u0148 Watana wepalylyk, halallyk, z\\u00e4hmets\\u00f6\\u00fderlik ruhunda terbi\\u00fdelenmegine, ylymly-bilimli, gi\\u0148 g\\u00f6z\\u00fdetimli \\u00fda\\u015flar\\u00a0\\u00a0 kemala gelmeginde uly i\\u015fler alnyp baryl\\u00fdar. Ertirki g\\u00fcn\\u00fcmizi\\u0148 da\\u00fdanjy bolup, \\u00fdurdumyzy belentliklere alyp gitjek\\u00a0 \\u00fda\\u015flara uly \\u00fcns beril\\u00fd\\u00e4r. Gara\\u015fsyzlygymyzy\\u0148 ilkinji g\\u00fcnlerinden ba\\u015flap, \\u00fda\\u015f nesilleri\\u0148 d\\u00f6wrebap terbi\\u00fde almagy \\u00fc\\u00e7in uly tagallalar edil\\u00fd\\u00e4n d\\u00f6w\\u00fcrde \\u00e4hli amatlyklary bolan bilim ojaklary, \\u00e7agalary\\u0148 sagdyn \\u00f6smegi \\u00fc\\u00e7in ni\\u00fdetlenen sport toplumlary, saglyklaryny goramak maksady bilen gurul\\u00fdan saglyk \\u00f6\\u00fdleri\\u0148 sany sanardan k\\u00e4ndir.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Muze\\u00fd gaznasyndan gurnalan sergide milliligimizi\\u0148 nusgasy bolan, \\u00e7aga durmu\\u015fyndan s\\u00f6z a\\u00e7\\u00fdan\\u00a0 \\u015fekilleri\\u0148 nakga\\u015f eserleri, \\u00c7agalary\\u0148 \\u00f6z elleri bilen \\u00e7ekilen suratlar, taryhy \\u00fdadyg\\u00e4rliklerden tapyllan \\u00e7aga o\\u00fdnawa\\u00e7lary, a\\u015fyklar, k\\u00fc\\u00fdze, t\\u00fcrkmen alaba\\u00fdyny\\u0148 \\u015fekili, g\\u00fcljagazy\\u0148 ekilen g\\u00f6rn\\u00fc\\u015fleri, \\u015fe\\u00fdle hem muze\\u00fd gaznasynda saklan\\u00fdan milli gymmatlyklar g\\u00f6rkezil\\u00fd\\u00e4r.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Berkarar d\\u00f6wleti\\u0148 t\\u00e4ze e\\u00fd\\u00fdamyny\\u0148 Galkyny\\u015fy d\\u00f6wr\\u00fcnde \\u00f6s\\u00fcp gel\\u00fd\\u00e4n \\u00fda\\u015f nesillere d\\u00f6wrebap terbi\\u00fde almaklary \\u00fc\\u00e7in gi\\u0148 m\\u00fcmkin\\u00e7ilikler d\\u00f6red\\u00fd\\u00e4n Gahryman Arkadagymyza, Arkadagly Gahryman Serdarymyza alky\\u015flarymyz \\u00e7\\u00e4ksizdir. Go\\u00fd Gahryman Arkadagymyzy\\u0148, Arkadagly Gahryman Serdarymyzy\\u0148 janlaryny\\u0148 sag, \\u00f6m\\u00fcrlerini\\u0148 uzak bolmagyny, il-\\u00fdurt b\\u00e4hbitli i\\u015flerini\\u0148 hemi\\u015fe rowa\\u00e7 bolmagyny arzuw ed\\u00fd\\u00e4ris.<\\/p>\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"8\",\"created\":\"2024-06-06 05:42:34\",\"created_by\":\"704\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2024-06-06 05:42:34\",\"modified_by\":null,\"checked_out\":null,\"checked_out_time\":null,\"publish_up\":\"2024-06-06 05:42:34\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_a