n d\\u00f6w\\u00fcrde \\u00e4hli amatlyklary bolan bilim ojaklary, \\u00e7agalary\\u0148 sagdyn \\u00f6smegi \\u00fc\\u00e7in ni\\u00fdetlenen sport toplumlary, saglyklaryny goramak maksady bilen gurul\\u00fdan saglyk \\u00f6\\u00fdleri\\u0148 sany sanardan k\\u00e4ndir.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img src=\\\"images\\/advportfoliopro\\/images\\/etnozaly.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Muze\\u00fd gaznasyndan gurnalan sergide milliligimizi\\u0148 nusgasy bolan, \\u00e7aga durmu\\u015fyndan s\\u00f6z a\\u00e7\\u00fdan\\u00a0 \\u015fekilleri\\u0148 nakga\\u015f eserleri, \\u00c7agalary\\u0148 \\u00f6z elleri bilen \\u00e7ekilen suratlar, taryhy \\u00fdadyg\\u00e4rliklerden tapyllan \\u00e7aga o\\u00fdnawa\\u00e7lary, a\\u015fyklar, k\\u00fc\\u00fdze, t\\u00fcrkmen alaba\\u00fdyny\\u0148 \\u015fekili, g\\u00fcljagazy\\u0148 ekilen g\\u00f6rn\\u00fc\\u015fleri, \\u015fe\\u00fdle hem muze\\u00fd gaznasynda saklan\\u00fdan milli gymmatlyklar g\\u00f6rkezil\\u00fd\\u00e4r.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Berkarar d\\u00f6wleti\\u0148 t\\u00e4ze e\\u00fd\\u00fdamyny\\u0148 Galkyny\\u015fy d\\u00f6wr\\u00fcnde \\u00f6s\\u00fcp gel\\u00fd\\u00e4n \\u00fda\\u015f nesillere d\\u00f6wrebap terbi\\u00fde almaklary \\u00fc\\u00e7in gi\\u0148 m\\u00fcmkin\\u00e7ilikler d\\u00f6red\\u00fd\\u00e4n Gahryman Arkadagymyza, Arkadagly Gahryman Serdarymyza alky\\u015flarymyz \\u00e7\\u00e4ksizdir. Go\\u00fd Gahryman Arkadagymyzy\\u0148, Arkadagly Gahryman Serdarymyzy\\u0148 janlaryny\\u0148 sag, \\u00f6m\\u00fcrlerini\\u0148 uzak bolmagyny, il-\\u00fdurt b\\u00e4hbitli i\\u015flerini\\u0148 hemi\\u015fe rowa\\u00e7 bolmagyny arzuw ed\\u00fd\\u00e4ris.<\\/p>\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"11\",\"created\":\"2024-06-06 08:00:40\",\"created_by\":\"704\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2024-06-07 05:01:17\",\"modified_by\":\"704\",\"checked_out\":\"704\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2024-06-07 05:00:30\",\"publish_up\":\"2024-06-06 05:37:40\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\