\u00e4\\u00e7esinde, i\\u015fler gyzgala\\u0148ly alnyp baryl\\u00fdar. Arkadag \\u015f\\u00e4herini\\u0148 d\\u00f6redilen g\\u00fcn\\u00fcne sanlyja g\\u00fcnden bir \\u00fdyl dol\\u00fdar. Arkadag \\u015f\\u00e4herini\\u0148 1-\\u00fdyllygy\\u00a0 mynasybetli T\\u00fcrkmenistany\\u0148 Zenanlar birle\\u015figini\\u0148 Merkezi Ge\\u0148e\\u015fini\\u0148, Arkadag \\u015f\\u00e4herini\\u0148 zenanlar b\\u00f6l\\u00fcmini\\u0148, Arkadag \\u015f\\u00e4herini\\u0148 Taryhy we \\u00fclk\\u00e4ni \\u00f6wreni\\u015f muze\\u00fdini\\u0148 gurnamagynda \\u00abArkadagly \\u00fdurdumda mirasyma sarpa bar\\u00bb atly sergi we tele\\u00fdazgyly gezelen\\u00e7 ge\\u00e7irildi.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0Dabara Arkadag \\u015f\\u00e4herinde i\\u015fje\\u0148 z\\u00e4hmet \\u00e7ek\\u00fd\\u00e4n zenanlarymyz gatna\\u015fdy. Olar \\u00f6zlerin bagtly zenandyklaryny, t\\u00e4ze \\u015f\\u00e4herde, t\\u00e4ze ja\\u00fdda, ma\\u015fgala agzybirliginde z\\u00e4hmet \\u00e7ek\\u00fd\\u00e4ndiklerini uly bu\\u00fdsan\\u00e7 bilen \\u00e7yky\\u015f etdiler. \\u015ee\\u00fdle aja\\u00fdyp d\\u00f6wri pe\\u015fge\\u015f beren Gahryman Arkadagymyza, Arkadagly Gahryman Serdarymyza \\u00f6zlerini\\u0148 \\u00e7\\u00e4ksiz minnetdarlygyny bildirdiler.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0\\u00a0 Asuda asmany\\u0148 astynda, parahat zemini\\u0148 \\u00fcst\\u00fcnde \\u015fe\\u00fdle aja\\u00fdyp \\u015f\\u00e4heri d\\u00f6redip beren Gahryman Arkadagymyzy\\u0148, Arkadagly Gahryman Serdarymyzy\\u0148 \\u00f6m\\u00fcrleri uzak, janlary sag, il-\\u00fdurt b\\u00e4hbitli alyp bar\\u00fdan i\\u015flerinde \\u00fcst\\u00fcnliklere hemra bolsun.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<div id=\\\"gtx-trans\\\" style=\\\"position: absolute; left: 429px; top: -15.8438px;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"11\",\"created\":\"2024-06-14 11:59:26\",\"created_by\":\"731\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2024-06-14 12:00:41\",\"modified_by\":\"731\",\"checked