0fclen go\\u015fgularyny\\u0148 \\u00fderle\\u015fdirilmegi \\u00fda\\u015f nesiller \\u00fc\\u00e7in has-da bu\\u00fdsan\\u00e7ly waka boldy. Bu g\\u00fcn Arkadag \\u015f\\u00e4herini\\u0148 Taryhy we \\u00fclk\\u00e4ni \\u00f6wreni\\u015f muze\\u00fdinde \\u00abArkadag\\u00bb tele\\u00fda\\u00fdlymy bilen bilelikde\\u00a0 Sahy Jepbarow adyndaky Arkadag \\u015f\\u00e4her \\u00fd\\u00f6rite sungat mekdebindeini\\u0148 mugallymlaryny\\u0148 we talyplaryny\\u0148 gatna\\u015fmagynda, \\u00abZenan zemini\\u0148 zynatyr\\u00bb atly wagyz-nesihat du\\u015fu\\u015fygy bolup ge\\u00e7di.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0\\u00a0 Dabarada \\u00abMagtymguly\\u00bb atly kitabyny\\u0148 \\u00e7apdan \\u00e7ykmagy hem-de ondaky zenanlara degi\\u015fli go\\u015fgulary\\u0148 a\\u00fddym bolup t\\u00fcrkmen halkyny\\u0148 kalbynda \\u00fda\\u015fa\\u00fdanlygy dogrusynda s\\u00f6hbetde\\u015flik boldy. Zenan zemini\\u0148 \\u00fda\\u015fa\\u00fd\\u015fy\\u0148 g\\u00f6zelligi. Bizi\\u0148 guwanjymyz, olary\\u0148 on barmagyny\\u0148 h\\u00fcn\\u00e4ri nesillerden-nesle ge\\u00e7ip \\u015fu g\\u00fcnlerimize gelip \\u00fdetenligi barada t\\u00e4sirli s\\u00f6hbetde\\u015flik gyzgala\\u0148ly ge\\u00e7di. Dabarany\\u0148 so\\u0148y a\\u00fddym-saza \\u00fdazdy.\\u00a0 Sahy Jepbarow adyndaky Arkadag \\u015f\\u00e4her \\u00fd\\u00f6rite sungat mekdebindeini\\u0148 talyplaryny\\u0148 Magtymguly Pyragyny\\u0148 s\\u00f6zlerine d\\u00f6redilen a\\u00fddymlary \\u00fderine \\u00fdetirdiler.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>T\\u00fcrkmenistanda umumadamzat gymmatlyklaryny\\u0148 hazynasyna uly go\\u015fant go\\u015fan halkymyzy\\u0148 medeni we ruhy mirasyny d\\u00fcn\\u00fd\\u00e4de gi\\u0148den wagyz etmek bo\\u00fdun\\u00e7a \\u00e4girt uly i\\u015fleri alyp bar\\u00fdan Gahryman Arkadagymyzy\\u0148, Arkadagly Gahryman Serdarymyzy\\u0148 janlaryny\\u0148 sag, \\u00f6m\\u00fcrlerini\\u0148 uzak bolmagyny, il-\\u00fdurt b\\u00e4hbitli i\\u015flerini\\u0148 hemi\\u015fe rowa\\u00e7lyklara beslenmegini arzuw ed\\u00fd\\u