<p>\\u00ddurdumyzy\\u0148 medeni\\u00fdetini, taryhyny d\\u00fcn\\u00fd\\u00e4 \\u00fda\\u00fdmakda k\\u00f6p i\\u015fler alnyp baryl\\u00fdar. Milli medeni\\u00fdetimizi\\u0148 \\u00f6smegi \\u00fc\\u00e7in gi\\u0148 \\u015fertler d\\u00f6redilen zamanada, d\\u00fcn\\u00fd\\u00e4 derejesine la\\u00fdyk gel\\u00fd\\u00e4n muze\\u00fd binalaryny\\u0148 gurlup ulanylmaga berilmegi, t\\u00fcrkmen halkyny\\u0148 taryhy tapyndylaryny ylmy ta\\u00fddan \\u00f6wrenmek, taryhy we medeni \\u00fdadyg\\u00e4rlikleri gorap saklamak, \\u00fda\\u015f nesillerimizi ata-balarymyzy\\u0148 gymmatly ruhy medeni-mirasyna hormat go\\u00fdmak, ruhunda terbi\\u00fdelemek muze\\u00fd i\\u015fg\\u00e4rlerini\\u0148 mukaddes borjy bolup dur\\u00fdarG\\u00f6zba\\u015fyny gadymy m\\u00fc\\u0148\\u00fdyllyklardan alyp ga\\u00fdd\\u00fdan Je\\u00fdtun, Altyndepe, Go\\u0148urdepe, Nusa\\u00fd, Merw, K\\u00f6ne\\u00fcrgen\\u00e7 medeni\\u00fdetleri bo\\u00fdnunda d\\u00fcr hazynany saklap oturan ruhy \\u00e7e\\u015fmedir. Taryha \\u00e7u\\u0148\\u0148ur g\\u00f6z \\u00fdetirmek \\u015fu g\\u00fcn\\u00fc\\u0148 ruhy d\\u00fcn\\u00fd\\u00e4sini a\\u00e7yp g\\u00f6rmekdir.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Medeni\\u00fdet we sungat i\\u015fg\\u00e4rlerini\\u0148 hem-de Magtymguly Pyragyny\\u0148 \\u015fygry\\u00fdet\\u00a0 g\\u00fcni \\u00a0be\\u00fdik s\\u00f6z ussady Magtymguly Pyragyny\\u0148 300 \\u00fdyllygy halkara derejesinde bellenip ge\\u00e7ilmegi halkymyzda bu\\u00fdsan\\u00e7 du\\u00fdgusyny d\\u00f6retdi.\\u00a0 Magtymguly Pyragy ge\\u00e7mi\\u015fi\\u0148, \\u015fu g\\u00fcn\\u00fc\\u0148, geljegi\\u0148 \\u015fahyrydyr. Magtymguly Pyragyny\\u0148 \\u015fahyrana d\\u00f6redijiligi, t\\u00fcrkmene mahsus be\\u00fdik ynsan h\\u00e4si\\u00fdetlerini jemle\\u00fd\\u00e4n \\u015fygyrlary\\u00a0 halky\\u0148 kalbynda \\u00fda\\u0148lan\\u00fdar. Magtymguly Pyragyny\\u0148\\u00a0 \\u015fygyry\\u00fdet ussatlygyny a\\u00e7yp g\\u00f6rkezmek maksady bilen ge\\u00e7iril\\u00fd\\u00e4n dabaralar \\u00fdurdumyzy\\u014