 Pyragyny\\u0148 300 \\u00fdyllygy halkara derejesinde bellenip ge\\u00e7ilmegi halkymyzda bu\\u00fdsan\\u00e7 du\\u00fdgusyny d\\u00f6retdi.\\u00a0 Magtymguly Pyragy ge\\u00e7mi\\u015fi\\u0148, \\u015fu g\\u00fcn\\u00fc\\u0148, geljegi\\u0148 \\u015fahyrydyr. Magtymguly Pyragyny\\u0148 \\u015fahyrana d\\u00f6redijiligi, t\\u00fcrkmene mahsus be\\u00fdik ynsan h\\u00e4si\\u00fdetlerini jemle\\u00fd\\u00e4n \\u015fygyrlary\\u00a0 halky\\u0148 kalbynda \\u00fda\\u0148lan\\u00fdar. Magtymguly Pyragyny\\u0148\\u00a0 \\u015fygyry\\u00fdet ussatlygyny a\\u00e7yp g\\u00f6rkezmek maksady bilen ge\\u00e7iril\\u00fd\\u00e4n dabaralar \\u00fdurdumyzy\\u0148 \\u00e7ar k\\u00fcnjeginde \\u00fda\\u00fdba\\u0148landy.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0Sergide milliligimizi\\u0148 nusgasy bolan, haly \\u00f6n\\u00fcmleri, el i\\u015fleri, \\u015fa\\u00fd-sepler, z\\u00e4hmet gurallary, dokma gurallary, keramika \\u00f6n\\u00fcmleri, taryhy gymmatlyklardan tapyndylar, kitaplar, etnografi\\u00fda zalyndaky milli gymmatlyklar, t\\u00fcrkmen durmu\\u015fyndan s\\u00f6z a\\u00e7\\u00fdan nakga\\u015f eserleri,\\u00a0 Magtymguly Pyragyny\\u0148 he\\u00fdkeli, keramika \\u00f6n\\u00fcmler \\u015fe\\u00fdle hem muze\\u00fd gaznasynda saklan\\u00fdan milli gymmatlyklar g\\u00f6rkezil\\u00fd\\u00e4r.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Milli mirasymyza\\u00a0 gi\\u0148 m\\u00fcmkin\\u00e7ilikler d\\u00f6red\\u00fd\\u00e4n Gahryman Arkadagymyza, Arkadagly Gahryman Serdarymyza alky\\u015flarymyz \\u00e7\\u00e4ksizdir. Go\\u00fd Gahryman Arkadagymyzy\\u0148, Arkadagly Gahryman Serdarymyzy\\u0148 janlaryny\\u0148 sag, \\u00f6m\\u00fcrlerini\\u0148 uzak bolmagyny, il-\\u00fdurt b\\u00e4hbitli i\\u015flerini\\u0148 hemi\\u015fe rowa\\u00e7 bolmagyny arzuw ed\\u00fd\\u00e4ris.<\\/p>\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"11\",\"created\":\"2024-06-20 10:11:46\",\"created_by\":\"731\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2024-06-20 10:28:00\",\"modified_by\":\"731\",\"checked_out\":\"731\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2024-06-20 10:25:06\",\"publis