slahaty we amaly-ha\\u015fam sungatyny\\u0148 eserlerini\\u0148 sergisi<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0\\u00a0 \\u00abP\\u00e4him-pa\\u00fdhas ummany Magtymguly Pyragy\\u00bb \\u00fdylynda, Arkadag \\u015f\\u00e4herinde ilkinji gezek bellenil\\u00fd\\u00e4n, Medeni\\u00fdet we sungat i\\u015fg\\u00e4rlerini\\u0148 hem-de Magtymguly Pyragyny\\u0148 \\u015fygry\\u00fdet\\u00a0 g\\u00fcn\\u00fcne bagy\\u015flanan Medeni\\u00fdet hepdeligi ba\\u015flady. Medeni\\u00fdet hepdeligini\\u0148 me\\u00fdilnamasy esasynda, muze\\u00fd h\\u00fcn\\u00e4rmenlerini gatna\\u015fmaklarynda <strong>\\u00ab<\\/strong>Muze\\u00fd gymmatlyklaryny hasaba almak we gorap saklamak bo\\u00fdun\\u00e7a d\\u00fcn\\u00fd\\u00e4 tejribesini\\u0148 m\\u00fcmkin\\u00e7ilikleri\\u00bb atly i\\u015f\\u00a0 maslahatyny\\u0148 we muze\\u00fd gymmatlyklaryny\\u0148 hem-de amaly-ha\\u015fam sungatyny\\u0148 eserlerini\\u0148 sergisini\\u0148 a\\u00e7yly\\u015f dabarasy boldy. Ba\\u00fdram\\u00e7ylyk dabarasyna wela\\u00fdatlary\\u0148 muze\\u00fd h\\u00fcn\\u00e4rmenleri, T\\u00fcrkmenistany\\u0148 D\\u00f6wlet medeni\\u00fdet merkezini\\u0148 D\\u00f6wlet muze\\u00fdini\\u0148, T\\u00fcrkmenistany\\u0148 \\u015eekillendiri\\u015f sungaty muze\\u00fdinden, \\u201cWatan mukaddesligi\\u201d muze\\u00fdinden, \\u201cG\\u00f6kdepe\\u201d milli muze\\u00fdinden, T\\u00fcrkmen d\\u00f6wlet medeni\\u00fdet institutyny\\u0148 mugallymlary we talyplary, T\\u00fcrkmen d\\u00f6wlet medeni\\u00fdet we sungat mekdebini\\u0148 mugallymlary we talyplary gatna\\u015fydylar.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>A\\u00e7yly\\u015f dabarasyny\\u0148 ba\\u015fynda Da\\u015foguz wela\\u00fdatyny\\u0148 Saparmyrat T\\u00fcrkmenba\\u015fy etrabyny\\u0148 D\\u00f6wkesen ge\\u0148e\\u015fligini\\u0148 \\u00fderli \\u00fda\\u015fa\\u00fdjylaryny\\u0148 Horezm\\u015falar d\\u00f6wr\\u00fcne degi\\u015fli tapylan altyn we k\\u00fcm\\u00fc\\u015f te\\u0148\\u0148eleri Arkadag \\u015f\\u00e4herini\\u0148 Taryhy we \\u00fclk\\u00e4ni \\u00f6wreni\\u015f muze\\u00fdini\\u0148 gaznasyna tab\\u015fyryldy. Ol t\\u00e4sin tapyndylary tapan ilde\\u015flerimize gymmatbahaly sowgatlar gow\\u015furyldy. Dabarada muze\\u00fd \\u00fdolba\\u015f\\u00e7ylary\\u0148, \\u00f6kde h\\u00fcn\\u00e4rmenleri\\u0148 muze\\u00fd gymmatlyklary dogrusynda gyzykly \\u00e7yky\\u015flary di\\u0148lendi. \\u00c7yky\\u015flarda Arkadag \\u015f\\u00e4herini\\u0148 Taryhy we \\u00fclk\\u00e4ni \\u00f6wreni\\u015f muze\\u00fdinde muze\\u00fd gymmatlyklaryny hasaba almak we gorap saklamak bo\\u00fdun\\u00e7a alnyp baryl\\u00fdan maksatla\\u00fdyn i\\u015fler barada, alnyp baryl\\u00fdan i\\u015flerde sanly ulgamy\\u0148 \\u00e4hmi\\u00fdeti dogrusynda, olary gorap saklamagy\\u0148 a\\u00fdratyn ugurlary hakynda, \\u015eekillendiri\\u015f sungatyny\\u0148 eserlerini gorap saklamakda talap edil\\u00fd\\u00e4n \\u015fertleri\\u0148 \\u00e4hmi\\u00fdeti babatda, muze\\u00fd gaznahanalaryny\\u0148 abzalla\\u015fdyryly\\u015fy hem-de muze\\u00fd gymmatlyklaryny \\u00fderle\\u015fdirmegi\\u0148 kadalary we tertibi hakynda hem t\\u00e4sirli \\u00e7yky\\u015flar boldy. \\u00a0Maslahaty\\u0148 has-da a\\u00fdratynlykly tarapy wideog\\u00f6rn\\u00fc\\u015f arkaly T\\u00dcRKSO\\u00dd halkara guramasyny\\u0148 Muze\\u00fdler birle\\u015figini\\u0148 ba\\u015f utga\\u015fdyryjysyny\\u0148, Gazagystan Respublikasyndan muze\\u00fd \\u00fdolba\\u015f\\u00e7ysyny\\u0148, T\\u00fcrki\\u00fde Respublikasyndan muze\\u00fd \\u00fdolba\\u015f\\u00e7ysyny\\u0148, \\u00d6zbegistan Respublikasyndan muze\\u00fd \\u00fdolba\\u015f\\u00e7ysyny\\u0148 onla\\u00fdn \\u00e7yky\\u015flaryna\\u00a0 we gutlaglaryna wideog\\u00f6rn\\u00fc\\u015f arkaly toma\\u015fa edildi. So\\u0148ra i\\u015f maslahatyna gatna\\u015fyjylary\\u0148 \\u00e4hlisini Arkadag \\u015f\\u00e4herini\\u0148 Taryhy we \\u00fclk\\u00e4ni \\u00f6wreni\\u015f muze\\u00fdini\\u0148 sergi-ekspozisi\\u00fdasy bilen tany\\u015fdyryldy.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"11\",\"created\":\"2024-06-23 11:29:59\",\"