aradaky milli m\\u00fcdirligini\\u0148 alymlarydyr, h\\u00fcn\\u00e4rmenleri, Ylymlar akademi\\u00fdasyny\\u0148 numizmatlary tarapyndan toplanan maglumatlara g\\u00f6r\\u00e4 altyn te\\u0148\\u0148eleri\\u0148 k\\u00e4birlerini\\u0148 \\u00fd\\u00fcz\\u00fcnde Horezm\\u015falar d\\u00f6wletini\\u0148 h\\u00f6k\\u00fcmdary Soltan Allaeddin Muhammedi\\u0148 we onu\\u0148 kakasy Soltan Teke\\u015fi\\u0148 atlaryny\\u0148 \\u00fdazylandygy anyklanyldy.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Altyn we k\\u00fcm\\u00fc\\u015f te\\u0148\\u0148eler \\u00e7aklamalara g\\u00f6r\\u00e4\\u00a0 K\\u00f6ne\\u00fcrgen\\u00e7li t\\u00fcrkmenleri\\u0148 guran kuwwatly d\\u00f6wletini\\u0148 XII-XIII asyrlaryny\\u0148 ba\\u015fynda g\\u00fcll\\u00e4p \\u00f6sen d\\u00f6wri bilen baglydyr. Tapylan gymmatlyklar Arkadag \\u015f\\u00e4herini\\u0148 Taryhy we \\u00fclk\\u00e4ni \\u00f6wreni\\u015f muze\\u00fdine tab\\u015fyryldy. Toplanan maglumatlarda tab\\u015fyrylan altyn te\\u0148\\u0148eler\\u00a0 muze\\u00fdi\\u0148 gaznasyny\\u0148 goruny ba\\u00fdla\\u015fdyrdy, \\u015fe\\u00fdle hem bu tapyndylary halk k\\u00f6p\\u00e7\\u00fcligine gi\\u0148den wagyz etmekde muze\\u00fdde birn\\u00e4\\u00e7e i\\u015fler amala a\\u015fyryldy. \\u00ddakynda Arkadag \\u015f\\u00e4herini\\u0148 Taryhy we \\u00fclk\\u00e4ni \\u00f6wreni\\u015f muze\\u00fdini\\u0148 h\\u00fcn\\u00e4rmenlerini\\u0148 we Arkadag \\u015f\\u00e4herini\\u0148 Jemgy\\u00fdet\\u00e7ilik guramalaryny\\u0148 bilelikde gurnamagynda \\u00a0\\u201cTaryhy\\u0148 yzlary\\u201d atly tegelek stolda s\\u00f6hbetde\\u015flik maslahaty ge\\u00e7irildi. S\\u00f6hbetde\\u015flikde bu tapyndylary\\u0148 taryhy we \\u00e4hmi\\u00fdeti dogrusynda g\\u00fcrr\\u00fc\\u0148 edildi.<\\/p>\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"2\",\"created\":\"2024-07-04 07:55:07\",\"created_by\":\"731\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2024-07-04 07:58:52\",\"modified_by\":\"731\",\"checked_out\":\"731\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2024-07-04 07:55:25\",\"publish_up\":\"2024-07-04 07:55:07\",\"p