dag \\u015f\\u00e4herini\\u0148 Taryhy we \\u00fclk\\u00e4ni \\u00f6wreni\\u015f muze\\u00fdini\\u0148 bilelikde gurnamagynda <strong>\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0<\\/strong>Ogulabat k\\u00e4b\\u00e4mizi\\u0148 on barmagyny\\u0148 d\\u00f6reden nepisliklerini wasp etmek maksady bilen \\u00abMa\\u015fgala mukaddesligi \\u00fd\\u00f6relg\\u00e4m, el h\\u00fcn\\u00e4rim g\\u00f6reld\\u00e4m\\u00bb atly \\u201ctegelek stolu\\u0148\\u201d ba\\u015fyndaky s\\u00f6hbetde\\u015flik ge\\u00e7irildi. S\\u00f6hbetde\\u015flige \\u00a0Berdimuhamet Anna\\u00fdew adyndaky Arkadag \\u015f\\u00e4herini\\u0148 mugallym\\u00e7ylyk orta h\\u00fcn\\u00e4r okuw mekdebini\\u0148 mugallymy, ilkinji Zenanlar guramasyny\\u0148 i\\u015fje\\u0148 agzasy G\\u00fcljana Gar\\u00fdagdy\\u00fdewa \\u00a0\\u015fe\\u00fdle-de Arkadag \\u015f\\u00e4herini\\u0148 Taryhy we \\u00fclk\\u00e4ni \\u00f6wreni\\u015f muze\\u00fdini\\u0148 uly ylmy i\\u015fg\\u00e4ri, k\\u00e4rde\\u015fler arkala\\u015fygyny\\u0148 ilkinji guramasyny\\u0148 i\\u015fje\\u0148 agzasy B\\u00e4g\\u00fcl Gylyjowa, Arkadag \\u015f\\u00e4herini\\u0148\\u00a0 \\u00fd\\u00f6ritele\\u015fdirilen 2-nji orta mekdebini\\u0148 mugallymy, k\\u00e4rde\\u015fler arkala\\u015fygyny\\u0148 ilkinji guramasyny\\u0148 i\\u015fje\\u0148 agzasy Enar Aga\\u00fdewa dagy gatna\\u015fdylar. Olar ene-mamalarymyzdan nesilme-nesil dowam edip gel\\u00fd\\u00e4n milli mirasymyzy\\u0148 gymmatlyklary dogrusynda gyzykly g\\u00fcrr\\u00fc\\u0148ler berdiler. Milli mirasymyzy\\u0148 nepisliklere si\\u0148ip giden gymmatlyklaryny gorap saklamakda muze\\u00fdde \\u00fderine \\u00fdetiril\\u00fd\\u00e4n i\\u015fler dogrusynda t\\u00e4sirli \\u00e7yky\\u015flar boldy. T\\u00fcrkmen zenanlaryny\\u0148 ruhy g\\u00f6zelliginden, \\u00e7eper ellerinden d\\u00f6r\\u00e4n nepis ke\\u015fde\\u00e7ilik sungatyny\\u0148 milli medeni mirasymyzy\\u0148 a\\u00fdrylmaz b\\u00f6legine \\u00f6wr\\u00fclip, k\\u00f6pasyrlyk milli d\\u00e4pleri dowam etdirip \\u00f6z gymmatyny \\u00fditirm\\u00e4n, e\\u00fdsem d\\u00f6wrebapla\\u015fyp h\\u00e4zirki g\\u00fcnlerimizde hem aja\\u00fdyplygy bilen\\u00a0 \\u00fdakymly t\\u00e4sir go\\u00fd\\u00fdandygy barada beren g\\u00fcrr\\u00fc\\u0148leri dabara gatna\\u015fanlarda t\\u00e4sir galdyrdy.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>T\\u00fcrkmenistanda umumadamzat gymmatlyklaryny\\u0148 hazynasyna uly go\\u015fant go\\u015fan halkymyzy\\u0148 medeni we ruhy mirasyny d\\u00fcn\\u00fd\\u00e4de gi\\u0148den wagyz etmek bo\\u00fdun\\u00e7a \\u00e4girt uly i\\u015fleri alyp bar\\u00fdan Gahryman Arkadagymyzy\\u0148, Arkadagly Gahryman Serdarymyzy\\u0148 janlaryny\\u0148 sag, \\u00f6m\\u00fcrlerini\\u0148 uzak bolmagyny, il-\\u00fdurt b\\u00e4hbitli i\\u015flerini\\u0148 hemi\\u015fe rowa\\u00e7lyklara beslenmegini arzuw ed\\u00fd\\u00e4ris.<\\/p>\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"11\",\"created\":\"2024-07-17 06:51:03\",\"created_by\":\"731\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2024-07-17 06:51:03\",\"modified_by\":null,\"checked_out\":null,\"checked_out_time\":null,\"publish_up\":\"2024-07-17 06:51:03\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\