img src=\\\"images\\/fpzw4zCDrbexht1FP9ts22nDXq2qo8sDHzUayhoDY8DTODXcV6b65fKFR75q-960x702.jpg\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>A\\u00e7yly\\u015f dabarasynda Da\\u015foguz wela\\u00fdatyny\\u0148 Saparmyrat T\\u00fcrkmenba\\u015fy etrabyny\\u0148 D\\u00f6wkesen ge\\u0148e\\u015fligini\\u0148 \\u201c\\u00ddedi howuz\\u201d di\\u00fdlip atlandyryl\\u00fdan \\u00f6ri me\\u00fddanyny\\u0148 takmynan 45-50 kilometr demirgazyk tarapynda ge\\u00e7\\u00fd\\u00e4n kerwen \\u00fdoluny\\u0148 ugrundaky \\u00f6ri me\\u00fddanlaryndan bu \\u00fderi\\u0148 \\u00fda\\u015fa\\u00fdjylary tarapyndan 18 sany altyn te\\u0148\\u0148eler, 3 sany k\\u00fcm\\u00fc\\u015f te\\u0148\\u0148eler we 61 sany altyn te\\u0148\\u0148eleri\\u0148 b\\u00f6lekleri, \\u015fe\\u00fdle hem 8 sany d\\u00fcrli re\\u0148kli tapyndylar tapyldy. T\\u00fcrkmenistany\\u0148 Taryhy we medeni \\u00fdadyg\\u00e4rlikleri goramak, \\u00f6wrenmek hem-de rejelemek baradaky milli m\\u00fcdirligini\\u0148 alymlarydyr, h\\u00fcn\\u00e4rmenleri, Ylymlar akademi\\u00fdasyny\\u0148 numizmatlary tarapyndan toplanan maglumatlara g\\u00f6r\\u00e4 altyn te\\u0148\\u0148eleri\\u0148 k\\u00e4birlerini\\u0148 \\u00fd\\u00fcz\\u00fcnde Horezm\\u015falar d\\u00f6wletini\\u0148 h\\u00f6k\\u00fcmdary Soltan Allaeddin Muhammedi\\u0148 we onu\\u0148 kakasy Soltan Teke\\u015fi\\u0148 atlaryny\\u0148 \\u00fdazylandygy anyklanyldy.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Altyn we k\\u00fcm\\u00fc\\u015f te\\u0148\\u0148eler \\u00e7aklamalara g\\u00f6r\\u00e4\\u00a0 K\\u00f6ne\\u00fcrgen\\u00e7li t\\u00fcrkmenleri\\u0148 guran kuwwatly d\\u00f6wletini\\u0148 XII-XIII asyrlaryny\\u0148 ba\\u015fynda g\\u00fcll\\u00e4p \\u00f6sen d\\u00f6wri bilen baglydyr. Tapylan gymmatlyklar Arkadag \\u015f\\u00e4herini\\u0148 Taryhy we \\u00fclk\\u00e4ni \\u00f6wreni\\u015f muze\\u00fdine tab\\u015fyryldy. Toplanan maglumatlarda tab\\u015fyrylan altyn te\\u0148\\u0148eler\\u00a0 muze\\u00fdi\\u0148 gaznasyny\\u0148 goruny ba\\u00fdla\\u015fdyrdy, \\u015fe\\u00fdle hem bu tapyndylary halk k