ml;sirli hem-de &ccedil;u\\u0148\\u0148ur p&auml;himli s&ouml;hbedi\\u0148 be&yacute;anydyr. Ma\\u015fgala ojagyna wepaly, watan&ccedil;y, z&auml;hmets&ouml;&yacute;er nesilleri &yacute;eti\\u015fdirmekde bitir&yacute;&auml;n i\\u015flerini be&yacute;an ed&yacute;&auml;n aja&yacute;yp setirleri\\u0148 mazmunyny &ouml;z&uuml;nde jemle&yacute;&auml;n bu kitap t&uuml;rkmen halkyny\\u0148 zenanlara go&yacute;&yacute;an sylag-hormatyny\\u0148 a&yacute;dy\\u0148 ny\\u015fany, islendik adam &uuml;&ccedil;in hem uly durmu\\u015f gollanmasy, &yacute;okary &yacute;a\\u015fa&yacute;y\\u015f mekdebidir.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>M&auml;hriban enelerimize, gelin gyzlarymyza &ccedil;&auml;ksiz sarpa go&yacute;&yacute;an, olary\\u0148 mertebesini belentde tutmakda, edep- ekramyna hormat bilen gara&yacute;an t&uuml;rkmen halkyny\\u0148 milli lideri Gahryman Arkadagymyzy\\u0148, Arkadagly Gahryman Serdarymyzy\\u0148 janlary sag, &ouml;m&uuml;rleri uzak, il-&yacute;urt b&auml;hbitli, d&uuml;n&yacute;&auml; &auml;hmi&yacute;etli tutumly i\\u015flerini\\u0148 hemi\\u015fe rowa&ccedil;lyklara beslenmegini arzuw ed&yacute;&auml;ris!<\\/p>\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"11\",\"created\":\"2024-07-31 11:21:40\",\"created_by\":\"731\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2024-08-14 05:54:57\",\"modified_by\":\"731\",\"checked_out\":\"731\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2024-08-14 05:52:38\",\"publish_up\":\"2024-07-31 11:21:40\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\