lias\":\"zenanlar-yasaysyn-goezelligi-atly-geplesik\",\"introtext\":\"Arkadag \\u015f\\u00e4herini\\u0148 Taryhy we \\u00fclk\\u00e4ni \\u00f6wreni\\u015f muze\\u00fdinde \\u201cZenanlar \\u00fda\\u015fa\\u00fd\\u015fy\\u0148 g\\u00f6zelligi\\u201d atly geple\\u015fik ge\\u00e7irildi\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\\r\\n              Milli \\u00fd\\u00f6relgelerimize a\\u00fdratyn \\u00e4hmi\\u00fdet beril\\u00fd\\u00e4n eziz Di\\u00fdarymyzda zenanlara uly hormat go\\u00fdul\\u00fdar, gelin-gyzlarymyzy\\u0148 mertebesi belentde tutul\\u00fdar. \\u00c7\\u00fcnki t\\u00e4ze taryhy e\\u00fd\\u00fdamymyzda hem t\\u00fcrkmeni\\u0148 belent ruhy gymmatlyklaryny\\u0148, gadymy d\\u00e4p-dessurlarymyzy\\u0148 we urp-adatlaryny\\u0148 a\\u00fdawly saklanylmagynda, milli \\u00fd\\u00f6relgelerimizi\\u0148 dowam etmeginde, edepli-ekramly nesilleri\\u0148 kemala gelmeginde zenanlarymyzy\\u0148 hyzmaty uludyr. T\\u00fcrkmen zenanlaryny\\u0148 ba\\u015farja\\u0148 ellerini\\u0148 aja\\u00fdyp sungaty bolan ke\\u00e7eler bizi\\u0148 \\u00fdurdumyzy\\u0148 taryhynda \\u00f6\\u00e7mejek yz galdyrypdyr. Arkadag \\u015f\\u00e4herini\\u0148 Taryhy we \\u00fclk\\u00e4ni \\u00f6wreni\\u015f muze\\u00fdinde hem \\u201cZenanlar \\u00fda\\u015fa\\u00fd\\u015fy\\u0148 g\\u00f6zelligi\\u201d atly geple\\u015fik ge\\u00e7irildi.T\\u00fcrkmen zenanlaryny\\u0148 zehin-ba\\u015farnygyny\\u0148, irginsiz z\\u00e4hmetini\\u0148 miwesi bolan bu senetleri synlany\\u0148da, aja\\u00fdyp bir du\\u00fdgyny ba\\u015fdan ge\\u00e7ir\\u00fd\\u00e4rsi\\u0148. \\u00c7\\u00fcnki g\\u00f6zelliklerden zynatly, \\u00f6z\\u00fcne \\u00e7ekiji, m\\u00e4hir-yhlasdan doly bolan bu senet dur\\u015funa ykbal hem sungatdyr. T\\u00fcrkmen zenanlary \\u00e4hli d\\u00f6w\\u00fcrde-de el i\\u015flerini nusgalyk derejede s\\u00fcnn\\u00e4l\\u00e4pdirler. El h\\u00fcn\\u00e4rini eneden-gyza ge\\u00e7irip dowam etdiripdirler. \\u00ddyllar ge\\u00e7digi\\u00e7e, olara t\\u00e4ze-t\\u00e4ze \\u00f6w\\u00fc\\u015fginler \\u00e7a\\u00fd