de s&uuml;nn&auml;l&auml;pdirler. El h&uuml;n&auml;rini nesilden-nesle ge&ccedil;irip, dowam etdiripdirler.Bu sungat asyrlar a\\u015fyp, &yacute;yllar ge&ccedil;digi&ccedil;e, t&auml;ze r&ouml;w&uuml;\\u015flere beslenip, has-da k&auml;mille\\u015fdiril&yacute;&auml;r. Zenanlary\\u0148 el i\\u015flerinde olary\\u0148 &ccedil;&auml;ksiz ussatlygy, irginsiz z&auml;hmeti, yhlasy g&ouml;r&uuml;n&yacute;&auml;r. &Ccedil;eper elli zenanlar nagy\\u015flara &ouml;z halkyny\\u0148 taryhyny, g&ouml;w&uuml;n matlabyny, arzuw-hy&yacute;allaryny si\\u0148dirip bilipdirler. Halky\\u0148 g&uuml;ndelik durmu\\u015fynda gi\\u0148den ulanylan we ruhy d&uuml;n&yacute;&auml;sine si\\u0148en ke&ccedil;elerimiz h&auml;zirki wagtda-da &yacute;urdumyzy\\u0148 d&uuml;rli k&uuml;njeklerinde &yacute;a\\u015famagyny dowam etdir&yacute;&auml;r. Bizi\\u0148 halkymyzy\\u0148 arasynda o\\u0148a hi&ccedil; wagt &auml;hmi&yacute;etini &yacute;itirmejek milli sungat h&ouml;km&uuml;nde garal&yacute;ar. Milli sungatymyzy, taryhymyzy, medeni&yacute;etimizi &ouml;wrnmekde we olara &yacute;a\\u015f nesillere gi\\u0148den wagyz etmekde uly tagallalar ed&yacute;&auml;n t&uuml;rkmen halkyny\\u0148 milli lideri Gahryman Arkadagymyza we Arkadagly Gahryman Serdarymyzy\\u0148 janlary sag, &ouml;m&uuml;rleri uzak bolsun! Il-&yacute;urt b&auml;hbitli, b&uuml;tind&uuml;n&yacute;&auml; adamzat &auml;hmi&yacute;etli be&yacute;ik i\\u015fleri hemi\\u015fe rowa&ccedil;lyklara beslensin!<\\/p>\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"2\",\"created\":\"2024-08-14 10:19:29\",\"created_by\":\"731\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2024-08-14 10:20:47\",\"modified_by\":\"731\",\"checked_out\":\"731\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2024-08-14 10:19:59\",\"publish_up\":\"2024-08-14 10:19:29\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"i