s_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_image\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/2024\\\\\\/08\\\\\\/16\\\\\\/IMG_20240816_115339.jpg\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_image_alt_txt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_article_format\\\":\\\"gallery\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_audio\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_gallery\\\":\\\"{\\\\\\\"helix_ultimate_gallery_images\\\\\\\":[\\\\\\\"images\\\\\\/2024\\\\\\/08\\\\\\/16\\\\\\/IMG_20240816_123205.jpg\\\\\\\"]}\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_video\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":9,\"ordering\":\"0\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"0\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"tk-TM\",\"xreference\":\"\",\"note\":\"\"}',0),(264,41,1,'','2024-08-22 11:08:52',731,6795,'cbc954b30ed1c6cdbf0f2fdb963c25bcb3e298fa','{\"id\":41,\"asset_id\":\"194\",\"title\":\"      \\u00abTaryhy\\u0148 k\\u00f6klerine si\\u0148en gadymy mekan\\u00bb atly sergi\",\"alias\":\"taryhyn-koeklerine-sinen-gadymy-mekan-atly-sergi\",\"introtext\":\"\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>&laquo;Taryhy\\u0148 k&ouml;klerine si\\u0148en gadymy mekan&raquo; atly muze&yacute; gymmatlyklaryndan bolan milli mirasymyza degi\\u015fli esbaplardan sergi gurnaldy.<\\/p>\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\\r\\n<p>&laquo;P&auml;him-pa&yacute;has ummany Magtymguly Pyragy&raquo; &yacute;yly mynasybetli Arkadagly Gahryman Serdarymyzy\\u0148 d&ouml;wlet sy&yacute;asatyny\\u0148 esasy ugurlaryny maksat edinip, &Auml;new \\u015f&auml;herini\\u0148 &ldquo;T&uuml;rki d&uuml;n&yacute;&auml;sini\\u0148 medeni pa&yacute;tagty&rdquo; di&yacute;lip yglan edilmegi mynasybetli, Arkadag \\u015f&auml;herini\\u0148 Taryhy we &uuml;lk&auml;ni &ouml;wreni\\u015f muze&yacute;inde &laquo;Taryhy\\u0148 k&ouml;klerine si\\u0148en gadymy mekan&raquo; atly muze&yacute; gymmatlyklaryndan bolan milli mirasymyza degi\\u015fli esbaplardan sergi gurnaldy. Ahal wela&yacute;atyny\\u0148 dolandyry\\u015f merkezi 2024-nji &yacute;ylda &laquo;T&uuml;rki d&uuml;n&yacute;&auml;ni\\u0148 medeni pa&yacute;tagty&raquo; di&yacute;lip atlandyrylan &Auml;new \\u015f&auml;heri &ouml;z&uuml;ni\\u0148 bahasyna &yacute;etip bolmajak taryhy-medeni mirasy bilen \\u015f&ouml;hratlan&yacute;ar. Orta asyrlarda Babagad di&yacute;lip atlandyrylan gadymy \\u015f&auml;heri\\u0148 &yacute;erlerinde ilkinji gazuw-agtary\\u015f i\\u015fleri di\\u0148e ge&ccedil;en asyry\\u0148 ba\\u015flarynda ge&ccedil;irilen hem bolsa, &Auml;newi\\u0148 taryhy &yacute;edi m&uuml;\\u0148 &yacute;yldan gowrak d&ouml;wri &ouml;z i&ccedil;ine al&yacute;ar. &Auml;new medeni&yacute;etini\\u0148 a&ccedil;ylmagyna amerikaly geolog Rafael Pampellini\\u0148 1903-nji &yacute;ylda T&uuml;rkmenistana amala a\\u015fyran ekspedisi&yacute;asy &yacute;ardam etdi. &Yacute;urdumyzy\\u0148 g&uuml;nortasynda &ccedil;&ouml;l &yacute;erlerde barlag ge&ccedil;irip, ol gadymy obalary\\u0148 galyndylaryny &yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;ykardy. Tiz wagtdan bu &yacute;erde ba\\u015flanylan gi\\u0148 gerimli gazuw-agtary\\u015f i\\u015fleri birn&auml;&ccedil;e t&auml;ze a&ccedil;y\\u015flary\\u0148 ba\\u015fyny ba\\u015flady. Bizi\\u0148 g&uuml;nlerimize &ccedil;enli 10 metr belentlikd&auml;ki ba&yacute;yrda &yacute;erle\\u015fen gadymy &Auml;new galasy saklanyp galypdyr. Galany\\u0148 diametri 300 metr t&ouml;weregi. Onu\\u0148 t&ouml;wereklerinde minaralary bolan galany\\u0148 diwarlaryny\\u0148 galyndylary, \\u015fe&yacute;le hem en&ccedil;eme asyrlary\\u0148 dowamynda galany\\u0148 &uuml;st&uuml;ni gum basan garymlary &yacute;erle\\u015f&yacute;&auml;r. &Ouml;zbolu\\u015fly desgalaryny\\u0148 hatarynda XV asyry\\u0148 ortalarynda gurlan Se&yacute;it Jemaletdini\\u0148 orta asyr metjidini\\u0148 harabalygy bar. Onu\\u0148 uly b&ouml;legi 1948-nji &yacute;yly\\u0148 &yacute;er titremesinde haraba&ccedil;ylyga &ouml;wr&uuml;lipdir. Binany\\u0148 1447&ndash;1457-nji &yacute;yllar d&ouml;wr&uuml;nde Horasany dolandyran te&yacute;mirleri\\u0148 h&ouml;k&uuml;mdary &nd