 bilen \\u015f&ouml;hratlan&yacute;ar. Orta asyrlarda Babagad di&yacute;lip atlandyrylan gadymy \\u015f&auml;heri\\u0148 &yacute;erlerinde ilkinji gazuw-agtary\\u015f i\\u015fleri di\\u0148e ge&ccedil;en asyry\\u0148 ba\\u015flarynda ge&ccedil;irilen hem bolsa, &Auml;newi\\u0148 taryhy &yacute;edi m&uuml;\\u0148 &yacute;yldan gowrak d&ouml;wri &ouml;z i&ccedil;ine al&yacute;ar. &Auml;new medeni&yacute;etini\\u0148 a&ccedil;ylmagyna amerikaly geolog Rafael Pampellini\\u0148 1903-nji &yacute;ylda T&uuml;rkmenistana amala a\\u015fyran ekspedisi&yacute;asy &yacute;ardam etdi. &Yacute;urdumyzy\\u0148 g&uuml;nortasynda &ccedil;&ouml;l &yacute;erlerde barlag ge&ccedil;irip, ol gadymy obalary\\u0148 galyndylaryny &yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;ykardy. Tiz wagtdan bu &yacute;erde ba\\u015flanylan gi\\u0148 gerimli gazuw-agtary\\u015f i\\u015fleri birn&auml;&ccedil;e t&auml;ze a&ccedil;y\\u015flary\\u0148 ba\\u015fyny ba\\u015flady. Bizi\\u0148 g&uuml;nlerimize &ccedil;enli 10 metr belentlikd&auml;ki ba&yacute;yrda &yacute;erle\\u015fen gadymy &Auml;new galasy saklanyp galypdyr. Galany\\u0148 diametri 300 metr t&ouml;weregi. Onu\\u0148 t&ouml;wereklerinde minaralary bolan galany\\u0148 diwarlaryny\\u0148 galyndylary, \\u015fe&yacute;le hem en&ccedil;eme asyrlary\\u0148 dowamynda galany\\u0148 &uuml;st&uuml;ni gum basan garymlary &yacute;erle\\u015f&yacute;&auml;r. &Ouml;zbolu\\u015fly desgalaryny\\u0148 hatarynda XV asyry\\u0148 ortalarynda gurlan Se&yacute;it Jemaletdini\\u0148 orta asyr metjidini\\u0148 harabalygy bar. Onu\\u0148 uly b&ouml;legi 1948-nji &yacute;yly\\u0148 &yacute;er titremesinde haraba&ccedil;ylyga &ouml;wr&uuml;lipdir. Binany\\u0148 1447&ndash;1457-nji &yacute;yllar d&ouml;wr&uuml;nde Horasany dolandyran te&yacute;mirleri\\u0148 h&ouml;k&uuml;mdary &ndash; Abul-Kasym Babyry\\u0148 h&ouml;k&uuml;mdarlyk eden d&ouml;wr&uuml;nde gurlandygy barada metjitde maglumatlar bolupdyr. &Auml;newi\\u0148 t&ouml;wereklerinde ge&ccedil;irilen gazuw-agtary\\u015f i\\u015flerin