\\u0148 medeni pa&yacute;tagty&raquo; di&yacute;lip yglan edilmegi mynasybetli, Arkadag \\u015f&auml;herini\\u0148 Taryhy we &uuml;lk&auml;ni &ouml;wreni\\u015f muze&yacute;inde &laquo;Taryhy\\u0148 k&ouml;klerine si\\u0148en gadymy mekan&raquo; atly muze&yacute; gymmatlyklaryndan sergi gurnaldy. Muze&yacute; gaznasyndan gurnalan sergide Hormatly Prezidentimizi\\u0148 &laquo;&Auml;new m&uuml;\\u0148&yacute;yllyklardan g&ouml;zba&rsquo;\\u015f al&yacute;an medeni&yacute;et&raquo; atly kitaby, taryhy tapyndylar, bina b&ouml;lekleri, \\u015fekillendiri\\u015f sungatyny\\u0148 eserleri, milli mirasymyza degi\\u015fli gymmatlyklar g&ouml;rkezil&yacute;&auml;r. T&uuml;rki medeni&yacute;eti\\u0148 halkara guramasyna (T&Uuml;RKSO&Yacute;) agza d&ouml;wletleri\\u0148 medeni&yacute;et ministrlerini\\u0148 hemi\\u015felik ge\\u0148e\\u015fini\\u0148 39-njy mejlisinde &Auml;new \\u015f&auml;herini\\u0148 2024-nji &yacute;ylda &laquo;T&uuml;rki d&uuml;n&yacute;&auml;sini\\u0148 medeni pa&yacute;tagty&raquo; di&yacute;lip yglan edildi. Medeni pa&yacute;tagt derejesi ba&yacute; ge&ccedil;mi\\u015fi t&uuml;rki d&ouml;wletleri\\u0148 d&ouml;re&yacute;i\\u015f taryhy bilen a&yacute;rylmaz baglany\\u015fykly bolan we h&auml;zirki wagtda t&uuml;rki d&uuml;n&yacute;&auml;ni\\u0148 umumy gymmatlygyna &ouml;wr&uuml;len, halklarymyzy\\u0148 medeni&yacute;etini, sungatyny d&uuml;n&yacute;&auml;de wagyz etmekde m&ouml;h&uuml;m orny e&yacute;ele&yacute;&auml;n gadymy&yacute;eti\\u0148 me\\u015fhur \\u015f&auml;herlerine beril&yacute;&auml;r. T&uuml;rkmen halkyny\\u0148 \\u015f&ouml;hratly taryhynda &ouml;zbolu\\u015fly orny e&yacute;ele&yacute;&auml;n &Auml;new \\u015f&auml;heri milli medeni we taryhy &yacute;adyg&auml;rlikleri &ouml;z&uuml;nde jemle&yacute;&auml;n gadymy \\u015f&auml;herleri\\u0148 biridir. 1904-nji &yacute;ylda &Auml;newi\\u0148 arheologik depelerinde ge&ccedil;irilen gazuw-barlag i\\u015fleri bu &yacute;erde eneolit d&ouml;wr&uuml;nde &yacute;a&yacute;ran ekeran&ccedil;ylyk medeni&yacute;eti barada k&ouml;p sanly gymmatly maglumatlary &yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;ykardy. \\u015eol gazuw-barlag i\\u015flerini\\u0148 dowamynda &yacute;adyg&auml;rligi\\u0148 bu d&ouml;wre degi\\u015fli medeni gatlaklarynda gadymy desgalary\\u0148 diwar galyndylary, z&auml;hmet gurallary, keramika &ouml;n&uuml;mleri bilen bir hatarda, ak bugda&yacute;y\\u0148 d&auml;neleri hem &yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;ykaryldy. Bu a&ccedil;y\\u015flardan so\\u0148ra, sebiti\\u0148 eneolit d&ouml;wr&uuml;ni\\u0148 arheologik medeni&yacute;eti &laquo;&Auml;new medeni&yacute;eti&raquo; ady bilen d&uuml;n&yacute;&auml;ni\\u0148 ylmy jemgy&yacute;et&ccedil;iligine &yacute;a\\u0148 saldy. XX asyry\\u0148 ortalarynda &Auml;new medeni&yacute;etine degi\\u015fli ba\\u015fga-da birn&auml;&ccedil;e &yacute;adyg&auml;rlikler &yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;ykaryldy. Orta asyrlarda Be&yacute;ik &Yacute;&uuml;pek &yacute;oluny\\u0148 ugrunda &yacute;erle\\u015fen &Auml;new galasy g&uuml;ll&auml;p &ouml;sen \\u015f&auml;her&ccedil;&auml; &ouml;wr&uuml;lipdir. Sergini\\u0148 a&ccedil;yly\\u015f dabarasyna Aba Anna&yacute;ew adyndaky Halkara At&ccedil;ylyk Akademi&yacute;asyny\\u0148, Saparmyrat Ata&yacute;ewi&ccedil; Ny&yacute;azow adyndaky T&uuml;rkmen oba hojalyk uniwersitetini\\u0148 mugallymlary, Arkadag \\u015f&auml;herini\\u0148 Aman Gulm&auml;mmedow adyndaky d&ouml;wlet drama teatryny\\u0148 sahna ussatlary, D&ouml;wletm&auml;mmet Azady adyndaky Arkadag \\u015f&auml;her kitaphanasyny\\u0148 h&uuml;n&auml;rmenleri gatna\\u015fdylar.<\\/p>\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"11\",\"created\":\"2024-08-22 10:58:56\",\"created_by\":\"731\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2024-08-23 06:38:41\",\"modified_by\":\"731\",\"checked_out\":\"731\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2024-08-23 06:37:46\",\"publish_up\":\"2024-08-22 10:58:56\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\