 \\u00f6s\\u00fc\\u015flere beslen\\u00fd\\u00e4r. \\u015eol sanda, ylym-bilim ulgamynda hem \\u015fanly menzillere, aja\\u00fdyp \\u00fcst\\u00fcnliklere e\\u00fde bolun\\u00fdar. Munu\\u0148 \\u00f6zi \\u00fdurdumyzda \\u00fda\\u015f nesilleri\\u0148 ylymly-bilimli, sagdyn, ruhubelent h\\u00fcn\\u00e4rmenler, k\\u00e4mil \\u015fahsy\\u00fdetler bolup \\u00fdeti\\u015fmegi babatda d\\u00f6wlet derejesinde edil\\u00fd\\u00e4n ta\\u00fdsyz tagallalary\\u0148 guwandyryjy netijeleridir. Arkadag \\u015f\\u00e4herini\\u0148 Taryhy we \\u00fclk\\u00e4ni \\u00f6wreni\\u015f muze\\u00fdinde Sa\\u00e7ly Dursunowa adyndaky Arkadag \\u015f\\u00e4herini\\u0148 lukman\\u00e7ylyk orta h\\u00fcn\\u00e4r okuw mekdebini\\u0148 talyplaryny\\u0148 hem-de Arkadag \\u015f\\u00e4herini\\u0148 3-nji orta mekdebini\\u0148 okuw\\u00e7ylaryny\\u0148 gatna\\u015fmagynda  muze\\u00fde gezelen\\u00e7 gurnaldy. \\r\\n   Munu\\u0148 \\u00fc\\u00e7in bagty\\u00fdar nesillerimizi\\u0148 Gahryman Arkadagymyza, peder \\u00fdoluny mynasyp dowam etdir\\u00fd\\u00e4n Arkadagly Serdarymyza ho\\u015fallygyny\\u0148 \\u00e7\\u00e4gi \\u00fdokdur. \\u00dda\\u015f nesillerimize d\\u00f6wrebap bilim bermek \\u00fc\\u00e7in \\u00e4hli \\u015fertleri d\\u00f6redip ber\\u00fd\\u00e4n t\\u00fcrkmen halkyny\\u0148 milli lideri Gahryman Arkadagymyzy\\u0148, Hormatly Prezidentimiz Arkadagly Gahryman Serdarymyzy\\u0148 janlary sag, \\u00f6m\\u00fcrleri uzak, il-\\u00fdurt b\\u00e4hbitli  b\\u00fctind\\u00fcn\\u00fd\\u00e4 adamzat \\u00e4hmi\\u00fdetli be\\u00fdik i\\u015fleri hemi\\u015fe rowana \\u00fdollarda rowa\\u00e7lyklara beslensin!\\r\\n\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"11\",\"created\":\"2024-09-01 09:30:29\",\"created_by\":\"731\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2024-08-31 09:53:58\",\"modified_by\":\"731\",\"checked_out\":\"731\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2024-08-31 09:53:44\",\"publish_up\":\"2024-09-01 09:30:29\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float